StakeWeight::createPermanentLock
├── when contract is paused
│   └── it should revert
└── when contract is not paused
    ├── when user already has a lock
    │   └── it should revert
    └── when user does not have a lock
        ├── when amount is zero
        │   └── it should revert
        ├── when duration is not in valid set
        │   └── it should revert
        └── when parameters are valid
            ├── it should create a permanent lock
            ├── it should set permanentUnlockDuration to duration
            ├── it should set slope to zero
            ├── it should calculate weighted bias based on duration
            ├── it should update total supply
            └── it should emit a Deposit event